# THE UNNAMED PROJECT — SIMULATOR

## What We Are Building
A simulation that demonstrates a living contribution economy.
This is Phase 1. The goal is to make anyone who watches it
understand the entire model within 30 seconds — no explanation needed.

## The Core Model To Demonstrate
- Contributions happen both ON the platform and OFF it
- An AI fairness agent scores all contributions regardless of source
- Scores decay as newer contributions advance the project
- Scores boost when others build directly on your work
- Revenue distributes in satoshis proportional to live share
- The agent finds external contributors - they don't find the agent
- No tokens. No equity. Nothing to sell. Only contribution.

## The Most Important Moment To Simulate
Someone on X posts something positive about the project.
They never visited the platform.
The agent detects it. Attributes it. Pays them.
They get notified. They had no idea.
THIS is the moment that explains everything.

## Sacred Rules For Every Feature
- The opening must start in complete darkness
- Numbers must always animate - never jump
- Satoshis must feel real and moving
- The "agent found them" external attribution event
  must hit differently from all other events
- A person who has never heard of Bitcoin must 
  understand this model in 30 seconds of watching

## What This Must NOT Look Like
- A crypto dashboard
- A hackathon project
- Anything corporate or safe

## What This MUST Look Like  
- The first time anyone has seen money work this way
- Alive. Sacred. Inevitable.
